name: Rodarte
biography: Laura (b.1979) and Kate Mulleavy (b.1980), sisters, launched their brand, Rodarte, in 2005. The name is their mother's maiden name. They won the 2008 CFDA Swarovski Emerging Womenswear Designer award, and was 2010 NDA winner. They both graduated from UC Berkeley, and have collaborated with major brands, such as Gap and Target.
